==English==
===Etymology===
Named after Min Min [[hotel]] which once stood nearby.
===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[min]] [[min]] [[lights]]|-}}
# [[Unexplained]] lights reportedly [[appearing]] in the sky near Boulia, [[western]] [[Queensland]], [[Australia]] for over 100 years. [[Possibly]] caused by [[reflection]]s of distant light in the dry air conditions.

